# EQUIPA Environment Configuration
# Copy to .env and populate with your infrastructure values.
# Copyright 2026, Forgeborn
#
# The orchestrator reads these via os.environ. You can also export them
# in your shell profile or set them in your systemd unit file.

# --- Core Paths ---
# Base directory where EQUIPA is installed (auto-detected if omitted)
# EQUIPA_BASE=/path/to/equipa

# Path to TheForge SQLite database (defaults to EQUIPA_BASE/theforge.db)
# THEFORGE_DB=/path/to/equipa/theforge.db

# Base directory containing all project repos (used by forge_config.json)
# PROJECT_BASE_DIR=/path/to/projects

# --- Network Hosts ---
# Primary build server
# BUILD_SERVER_HOST=your.build.server.ip

# Primary VPS (public-facing apps)
# PRIMARY_VPS_HOST=your.primary.vps.ip

# Secondary app VPS
# APP_VPS_HOST=your.app.vps.ip

# E-commerce production server
# ECOMMERCE_HOST=your.ecommerce.ip

# Hypervisor host
# HYPERVISOR_HOST=your.hypervisor.ip

# --- SSH ---
# SSH user for remote operations
# SSH_USER=your_username

# SSH key for remote operations
# SSH_KEY_PATH=~/.ssh/id_ed25519

# --- Ollama ---
# Base URL for the Ollama API
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434

# Default Ollama model
# OLLAMA_MODEL=qwen3.5:27b

# --- API Keys ---
# Anthropic API key (for autoresearch tiers 2/3 and ForgeSmith)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Training ---
# Directory containing training result markers
# TRAINING_RESULTS_DIR=/path/to/training-results

# ForgeSmith training data and output directories
# FORGESMITH_DATA_DIR=/path/to/forgesmith
# FORGESMITH_OUTPUT_DIR=/path/to/forgesmith/output

# --- MCP ---
# Path to the uvx binary for MCP server
# UVX_PATH=/path/to/uvx
